### Banking Transactions API - Sample Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

### ========================================
### Health Check
### ========================================

GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ========================================
### TRANSACTIONS
### ========================================

### Create a deposit to ACC-12345
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create another deposit to ACC-67890
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create a transfer from ACC-12345 to ACC-67890
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Create a withdrawal from ACC-12345
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### List all transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions

### Filter transactions by account
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### Filter transactions by type
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?type=transfer

### Filter transactions by date range
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2025-12-31

### Combine multiple filters
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=deposit

### Get transaction by ID (replace with actual ID from previous responses)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/txn-12345678

### ========================================
### ACCOUNTS
### ========================================

### Get balance for ACC-12345
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Get balance for ACC-67890
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-67890/balance

### Calculate interest with default parameters (5% for 30 days)
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/interest

### Calculate interest with custom rate and days
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/interest?rate=0.08&days=90

### Calculate interest with 10% annual rate for 365 days
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/interest?rate=0.10&days=365

### ========================================
### VALIDATION ERRORS
### ========================================

### Invalid amount (negative)
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": -100,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid amount (too many decimals)
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.999,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid currency
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "XYZ",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid account format
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "12345",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid type
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "invalid"
}

### Missing required fields for transfer
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### ========================================
### 404 ERRORS
### ========================================

### Non-existent transaction
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/txn-nonexistent

### Non-existent account balance
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-ZZZZZ/balance

### Non-existent account interest
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-ZZZZZ/interest
